7. **mcp-server.ts tool** -- CLI tool definition
8. **Session end updates** -- mcp-queries.ts, mcp-route.ts, http-client.ts
9. **Context builder** -- Enhanced read context

Steps 1-3 are foundation. Steps 4-7 are the core feature. Step 8 is session integration. Step 9 is an enhancement.

