103→    "Check if an existing decision in the graph answers your question. Use before making a new decision — the graph may already have the answer from a previous agent or human.",
104→    {
105→      question: z.string().describe("The question you need answered (e.g. 'Should this endpoint use REST or tRPC?')"),
